- Kỹ năng làm việc nhóm;
- Kỹ năng tổ chức và quản lý thời gian;
- Tự học và tự trau dồi kiến thức;
- Tư duy logic.
5. Thái độ, phẩm chất:
- Thái độ nhiệt huyết với công việc;
- Trung thực và đáng tin cậy;
- Cẩn thận, tỉ mỉ, nhạy bén;
- Bảo mật thông tin.

Job Description:
- To conduct legal works in relation to the day-to-day business and operations of the company in timely manner to protect the interest of the company. Specific works include, but not limited to, the following key tasks:
+ Provide strategic advice for all business (other than funding activities) and projects of the company (e.g., core banking activities, credit cards, insurance, marketing, etc.);
+ Research, analyze and provide legal consultation for various aspects during operations of the company;
+ Prepare, draft, revise, review and/or provide comments on all agreements, templates, internal regulations and/or other documents related to the Company;
+ Participate in the contract negotiation and execution of the Company;
+ Represent the Company in the litigation and other legal procedures involving the Company (where necessary);
+ Support the operations of Anti-Fraud team from legal perspective;
+ Provide Legal Update of new Regulations as well as translation of contracts and other materials (where necessary);
+ Assist the Funding Legal team and Treasury team in funding activities (if required);
+ Support other departments of the company in all legal matters;
- Be responsible in administer and make decision in certain areas as being assigned;
- Review and provide advice/supports to Senior Legal Executive, Legal Executive, Legal Specialist, and Legal Officer to maintain high-quality results as being assigned;
- To participate in and support the Head of Business Legal/ Business Legal Manager in the design and set-up of new products, customer journeys and processes, especially the ones with digital and modern orientation, using smart and innovative methods/ tools/ market practices as being assigned;
- To support Head of Business Legal in team management;
- To independently on behalf of Business Legal lead big projects from legal perspective; and
- Other tasks as may be assigned by the Chief Legal and Compliance Officer.

Job Requirements:
